description:
WoX is a launcher for Windows that simply works. It's an alternative to Alfred and Launchy.

A full-featured launcher, access programs and web contents as you type. Be more productive ever since.
1. fix more uwp load 2. performance improvement for starup 3. performance improvement for first search 4. up to 100 times speedup for query and program/win32/uwp index 5. this will be the last prerelease before stable release.
